      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites can make your explosives even deadlier by clustering your grenades and even potentially replicating them. When using your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.LLNp1urkLncOxgsb]{Gear Array (Ex)} to form a weapon that uses grenades as ammunition, you can give the weapon the cluster<sup>AR</sup> (5 ft.) special weapon property. This increases to cluster (10 ft.) at level 15. When you use a weapon formed from your gear array to make a cluster attack with non-magical grenades with an item level no greater than your level, you can spend a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{Nanite Surge (Ex)} to reduce the number of grenades expended by 1.</p>"
